metadata.name: Sól Guinevere, 2122
metadata.description:
If the very first fairy-tales were written in the future, what would the stories be?
___

Sól Guinevere lives in the land of Golden Star where everything from the buildings, to the plants, animals, and clothes are comprised of stardust. Celestial birds carry messages from the heavens...will the one that's being delivered bring her joy or sorrow?
___

Created for World of Women Season 7 ArtDrop
